<li>See the CKS topics on <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/urinary-tract-infection-children/\">Urinary tract infection - children</a> and <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/constipation-in-children/\">Constipation in children</a> for information on managing these conditions.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Arrange referral to a paediatrician or an enuresis clinic</strong> if a <a class=\"topic-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/bedwetting-enuresis/background-information/causes/\">cause</a> cannot be managed in primary care or is not clearly identified.</li></ul><!-- end field 20e253e1-cb22-4252-911b-6f99dfa0b5da --><!-- end item ca9cab49-9a62-4e2d-931e-6187cb0cd1e1 -->","subChapters":[{"id":"b6cedda1-acc1-5a1e-bfe4-13df4648b133","slug":"basis-for-recommendation-d99","fullItemName":"Basis for recommendation","depth":4,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 6a56784e-11f7-490f-b51d-382ecbc89ade --><h4>Basis for recommendation</h4><!-- end field 6a56784e-11f7-490f-b51d-382ecbc89ade -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item d999fb1d-963f-476a-8103-eaa15f64284f --><!-- begin field 37847c0c-123c-4291-9fba-15c6656f6a6f --><p>These recommendations are based largely on the National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE) guideline <em>Nocturnal enuresis: the management of bedwetting in children and young people </em>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/bedwetting-enuresis/references/\">National Clinical Guideline Centre, 2010</a>]. The <a href=\"https://www.nice.org.uk/guidance/cg111/resources/2018-surveillance-of-bedwetting-in-under-19s-nice-guideline-cg111-6599305837/chapter/Overview-of-2018-surveillance-methods?tab=evidence\" data-hyperlink-id=\"9ba1172e-d33d-4848-9766-ab8500cf164b\">2018 NICE surveillance review</a> did not find sufficient new evidence to warrant an update of the guideline.</p><!-- end field 37847c0c-123c-4291-9fba-15c6656f6a6f --><!-- end item d999fb1d-963f-476a-8103-eaa15f64284f -->","subChapters":[]}]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}